cs.LO, cs.AI, cs.SY, cs.PL, cs.DS

Reasoning: 
- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on formal synthesis of control policies for finite Markov decision processes with temporal logic constraints. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper deals with generating control policies automatically. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is another possible category as the paper deals with control policies for Markov decision processes. 
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is a possible category as the paper may involve programming languages used to implement the algorithm. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is another possible category as the paper involves developing an algorithm for optimal control of Markov decision processes.
